  <entry>
    <title>JSON数据格式化后在前端页面展示</title>
    <url>/2021/06/06/JSON%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%8C%96%E5%90%8E%E5%9C%A8%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h5 id="将-JSON-数据格式化后展示在前端页面或文本域中"><a href="#将-JSON-数据格式化后展示在前端页面或文本域中" class="headerlink" title="将 JSON 数据格式化后展示在前端页面或文本域中"></a>将 <code>JSON</code> 数据格式化后展示在前端页面或文本域中</h5><span id="more"></span>

<p>在做公司的一个需求，需要以 <code>json</code> 格式展示到文本域中，心里想着：这还不简单嘛，一个  <code>JSON.stringify()</code>   搞定完成。结果领导看了之后，让我将数据格式化一下，（参考在编辑器中的<code>json</code>格式）展示出来，一番百度之后，有了下面的代码….这里记录一下~</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> repeat (s, count) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Array</span>(count + <span class="number">1</span>).join(s)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    formatJson (json) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">var</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        il = <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        tab = <span class="string">&quot;    &quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        newJson = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        indentLevel = <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        inString = <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        currentChar = <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">for</span> (i = <span class="number">0</span>, il = json.length; i &lt; il; i += <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        currentChar = json.charAt(i);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">switch</span> (currentChar) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;[&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!inString) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += currentChar + <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span> + <span class="built_in">this</span>.repeat(tab, indentLevel + <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">              indentLevel += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += currentChar</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#125;&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;]&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!inString) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              indentLevel -= <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span> + <span class="built_in">this</span>.repeat(tab, indentLevel) + currentChar</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += currentChar</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;,&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!inString) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += <span class="string">&quot;,\n&quot;</span> + <span class="built_in">this</span>.repeat(tab, indentLevel)</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += currentChar</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;:&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!inString) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += <span class="string">&quot;: &quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += currentChar</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27; &#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;\t&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (inString) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              newJson += currentChar</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&quot;&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (i &gt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; json.charAt(i - <span class="number">1</span>) !== <span class="string">&#x27;\\&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              inString = !inString</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            newJson += currentChar;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">default</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            newJson += currentChar;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> newJson</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    getFormatData (json) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">var</span> json = json + <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (json.indexOf(<span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#x27;</span>) == -<span class="number">1</span> &amp;&amp; json.indexOf(<span class="string">&#x27;[&#x27;</span>) == -<span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> json;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> (<span class="built_in">this</span>.formatJson(json));</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 在 Vue 项目中使用只需要this.getFormatData(json)即可</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
